{
  "stem": "13690.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think that once, also, my brother went and bought some medication in a drugstore.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I think the Gentile did it-- I mean, the man, Mr.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Placzek did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He brought some medication.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Also, one of the incident that I do remember, that we were always given food at a given hour.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "At one time, I was just-- the house, like I stated, was not finished.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I walked over to the corner of the, so to say, of the attic, and looking down if Mr. or Mrs.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Placzek put the food already down next to the ladder.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "While I'm looking down, a little boy stares just straight into my eyes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he starts to scream.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He says, 'Mrs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Placzek!'",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Placzek is upstairs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she says, 'Yes?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh, that's wonderful.' Then all of a sudden, this Mr.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Placzek comes in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He comes home through the door.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So the little boy said, 'How did you fly down from the roof?' So I can tell you one thing-- we really were very panicky after that little boy.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were thinking, if he gets home and goes home, what kind of story he will make up, and what will he do, and what will he say?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we constantly lived in fear.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We always were worried about what the next hour, not the next day, will bring.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Also, one of the most important thing is that we had [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the situation of-- of that my brother went out one day.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were in line of communications with relatives that were in a village, also in hiding.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they wrote to us if we could help give money for a cousin which was given away, and also by a Gentile family.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
